sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as Detec Agent
    participant GW as DetecGateway<br/>TCP 8001
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>HTTP 8000
    participant DB as Database
    participant EDR as CrowdStrike
    participant WH as Webhooks

    Note over Agent,API: TCP Binary Protocol Flow

    Agent->>GW: AUTH (api_key, hostname, version)
    GW->>DB: Validate API key, upsert endpoint
    DB-->>GW: endpoint_id
    GW-->>Agent: AUTH_OK (session_id, endpoint_id)

    loop Every scan interval
        Agent->>Agent: Run scanners, score confidence, evaluate policy
        Agent->>GW: EVENT (tool, confidence, decision)
        GW->>DB: Persist event
        GW->>EDR: Enrich detection (if enabled)
        EDR-->>GW: EDR telemetry
        GW->>DB: Update rescored event
        GW->>WH: Dispatch webhook (async)
        GW-->>Agent: ACK
    end

    loop Heartbeat interval
        Agent->>GW: HEARTBEAT (status, uptime)
        GW->>DB: Update last_seen_at
        GW-->>Agent: HEARTBEAT_ACK (posture)
    end

    Note over GW,Agent: Server-initiated push
    GW->>Agent: POSTURE_PUSH (passive/audit/active)
    Agent-->>GW: COMMAND_ACK
    GW->>Agent: POLICY_PUSH (updated rules)

    Note over Agent,API: HTTP REST Flow (alternate transport)

    Agent->>API: POST /api/events (JSON, X-Api-Key)
    API->>DB: Persist event
    API->>EDR: Enrich detection
    API->>WH: Dispatch webhook
    API-->>Agent: 200 OK

    Agent->>API: POST /api/endpoints/heartbeat
    API->>DB: Update last_seen_at
    API-->>Agent: 200 OK (posture in body)

    Note over API,DB: Dashboard interaction
    participant UI as React Dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /api/endpoints (Bearer JWT)
    API->>DB: Query
    DB-->>API: Results
    API-->>UI: JSON response
